name: Butcher Shop - Death On Top Series 07
description:
Saturn was the first to taste this modern diet: children-based.
Have your cows and pigs replaced, human meat shall be embraced!

 We were graced with cheeky cheeks, fleshy lips instead of beaks. Why should we then go to waste and not on top of platters placed?

Heel and toe we’ll use for soup, peel the skin, wash the poop. Scoop the brains into a ball, make them really really small.
Breast and chests we’ll save the best, have them dressed in herbs for guests

"If they knock for your arrest, let it go I would suggest."

After all these meaty suits are not that different from the fruits: they both prime and they both rot, you can put them in a pot.  Cold or hot! Medium rare! The recipes that we share! Use your body, use your hair! Use the parts you have to spare!

 It’s not a trend like avocado, the ancient art of the asado. You might end up coronado and be the one descuartizado.  Have a prize for you size, for your beauty, or your thighs! You might be worth a higher price if we could only disguise the flies.

Serve them, serve them, serve them all! Be the cherry of the ball! Let us market parts of you: “Look out there, there’s a queue!” Lend your body for the stew cause their hunger only grew! Lend you body, oh you fool, you are our star, you are our fuel!

KILL COUNT +10
